      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T13:29:40Z",
      "messageBody": "Add state management and workspace context to Harness v1 so sessions can expose request state and workspace tools natively during the v1 migration.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
