        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T13:29:40Z",
      "messageBody": "Remove changesets for the Harness v1 state and workspace work because changelog entries are not needed yet.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
