          "name": "Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5)"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T13:30:03Z",
      "messageBody": "Keep the currently selected model when HarnessCompat switches between v1 sessions so thread changes do not reset back to the mode default.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
      "messageHeadline": "fix(mastracode): preserve model when switching threads",
      "oid": "6d0d6c404f3b059978e645d12440f2fc304faa5e"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-06-02T19:41:30Z",
