          "name": "Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5)"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T17:53:59Z",
      "messageBody": "Move v1 harness task state out of session records, keep live run state ephemeral, and collapse pending work into a single ordered record field. This keeps the stored session shape closer to the actual durable contract while preserving restart-safe pending records.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
      "messageHeadline": "refactor(core): simplify harness v1 session records",
      "oid": "c41f576385ebd527d40fc01efa8cfc8975fb897d"
    },
