          "login": "",
          "name": "Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5)"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T18:08:26Z",
      "messageBody": "Restore the GitHub Signals processor wiring that was dropped during the Harness v1 rebase, and adapt HarnessCompat skill activation to the v1 name-only skill API.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
      "messageHeadline": "fix(mastracode): restore GitHub signals compat",
      "oid": "c82f0c63ea28c9ab351233cf135a65d62330815c"
